Jamp, Just another mp3 player?
  Ok, its not really a player. Actualy Jamp is a http-streaming script
  with a lot of features:
  * XML based skins
  * HTTP/IP/Login authentication
  * Any old number of music folders
  * Access of music files via HTTP over symlinks
  * Each static file which is accessed will be cached for faster load next time
  * Temporary and static playlists for each user
  * Multi language support
  * Shoutbox for user communication
  * Bugs are in design

  Requirements:
  * Linux ;-)
  * Apache (only testet with it)
  * MySql
  * PHP
